snippet.title: Johnny Depp “TMZ kitchen video” finally released in its entirety
snippet.description:
After Amber Heard filed for divorce, obtained a temporary restraining order, and claimed Johnny Depp has physically abused her in 2016, a video was leaked by TMZ appearing to show Johnny Depp in his kitchen, slamming cupboard doors and using colorful language. 

Since then, this clip has repeatedly been cited by Amber Heard supporters as “proof” Johnny was abusive. However, it was cut short at the beginning and end and was never shown in its entirety, until the final day of the Johnny Depp VS NGN trial in London, as part of team Depps’ closing submissions. 

Fast forward to 0:46 if you want to skip the introduction. 

Credit to Nick Wallis for this footage. Follow him on Twitter at @NickWallis 

Full court documents including closing submissions available on www.nickwallis.com 



#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #JusticeForJohnnyDepp #TMZ
